<h2>Reset Database</h2>

<div class="warning-box" style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 2px solid #ffc107; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
  <h3 style="color: #856404; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ WARNING</h3>
  <p style="color: #856404; font-size: 16px;">
    This action will <strong>permanently delete ALL data</strong> in the database and recreate all tables with sample data.
  </p>
  <p style="color: #856404; font-size: 16px;">
    <strong>This action cannot be undone!</strong>
  </p>
</div>

<h3>What will happen:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>All horses will be deleted</li>
  <li>All races will be deleted</li>
  <li>All support cards will be deleted</li>
  <li>All sparks will be deleted</li>
  <li>All race entries will be deleted</li>
  <li>All horse-spark assignments will be deleted</li>
  <li>Sample data will be inserted</li>
</ul>

<form method="POST" action="/reset">
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-delete" style="background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px;">
    ⚠️ Confirm Reset Database
  </button>
  <a href="/" class="btn btn-cancel" style="margin-left: 10px;">Cancel</a>
</form>